title: Blade.Runner.2049.[ENGLISH.AUDIO].by.Amiga.500.RuLeZzz
description: English Audio ONLY (raw) from the new and excellent sequel film: Blade Runner 2049 Here is hoping one of the many inevitable non-English cam releases will quickly snap this up (please, use [email protected]) so others who speak English will finally have a movie to watch sooner than later. Way too often these days new English cam releases are getting harder and harder to find without having to wait 1-2 months after first theater releases. My apologies for the parts where it gets so loud the audio washes out (doesnt happen often though). The damn theater speakers were so loud that even in person they too were making the same washed out sounds. Chill guys and turn down the volume. I don't want to be permanently deaf
